SubAtomic Subscriptions Manager.

Stay on top of all your subscriptions with SubAtomic, a robust and user-friendly subscription management application. With SubAtomic, you can manage, organize, and track all your subscriptions in one location, taking control of your recurring expenses.

Features
- One click access right in the side panel
- Quickly import info from current tab
- Sync between your browsers
- Completely private all data is stored on your google account
- Estimate monthly spendings
- and more
